description:
In part one of this two part series I look at four dreadful murders which took place in Clydach, near Swansea, South Wales in 1999\. The sheer savagery and brutality of the murders, which wiped out three generations of the same family, rocked the local community and are still widely spoken about today.&#13;
&#13;
